{"word":"ἀποτρίβω","slug":"ἀποτρίβω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποτρίβω</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to wear out</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to rub clean, to rub down</i> a horse, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to rub off</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to get rid of</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b>: <i>to decline, reject</i>, <el>τὴν πεῖραν</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}